{
  "doc_id": "52836",
  "text": "Blastocysts were collected from matings using Kit W-lacZ/+ [CITATION_1] , Pdgfra H2B-GFP/+ [CITATION_2] , Pdgfra fl/fl [CITATION_3] and ROSA26 CreERT2/CreERT2 [CITATION_4] alleles. Blastocysts were cultured individually for 5 days in 4-well plates on MEFs in ES cell media containing LIF. ICMs were dissociated in 0.25% trypsin-EDTA, and passaged into 24-well dishes containing MEFs. Media were changed every 2 days. Cells were passaged 7-10 days later into fresh 24-well plates until confluency, then cultured in the absence of MEFs and genotyped by PCR.",
